posting_body: ['WE HAVE A RENT TO OWN PROGRAM EASY TO  QUALIFY!', 'Quick move in.', 'If you are an independent worker have low credit or background issues and have problems finding a place to settle with your family, do not hesitate call me or TEXT me, I am a rental expert in South Florida, I will find a property for you and get you approved.', 'WE HAVE A RENT TO OWN PROGRAM with credit score of over 550, we will buy any property CASH for you  up tp $600,000 and then rent it to you for 1 to 3 years until you can get ready to purchase it, it will save some of your rent money towards the purchase ( about 25% of payment).', 'Looking for for a place to call home?', 'Look no further!', 'Beautiful and Spacious 4 bedroom 2 bathroom home with a 2 car garage in the much desired area of Calusa Club Estates available for RENT!', 'Completely updated & Modern with a gorgeous open floor plan.', 'Features include Stainless Steel appliances, washer and dryer, large family room.', 'CALL ME OR TEXT ME', 'I RESPOND INMIDIATELLY!!', 'show contact info', ')', '""EASY SOLUTIONS REALTY LLC ""']
